<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Natural gas bills can become a significant cost item, especially in the winter months due to the need for heating. The natural gas bill for an average student ranges from 5 USD to 10 USD per month. Factors affecting natural gas costs are:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
