<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey remains an attractive destination for international students due to its educational opportunities and cost of living. Knowing the average costs of electricity, water and natural gas bills will help students manage their budgets better. If you are considering studying in Turkey, take advantage of these opportunities and be open to new experiences!</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-documents-are-required-for-university-education-in-turkey">What documents are required for university education in Turkey?</h3>



