<li><strong>Categorize Your Expenses</strong>: Write down your accommodation, food, transportation, entertainment and education expenses separately.</li>



<li><strong>Set Monthly Spending Limits</strong>: Set how much you can spend for each category.</li>



<li><strong>Track Your Expenses</strong>: Record your expenses regularly and review your budget.</li>
</ul>



