<p class="wp-block-paragraph">State gyms offer affordable sports facilities and a variety of sports activities. Special discounts are also available for students.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-participate-in-sporting-events">How to participate in sporting events?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can expand your social circle and gain new experiences by participating in various sporting events such as local marathons, sports festivals and university events.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-the-benefits-of-doing-sports-in-turkey">What are the benefits of doing sports in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to improving physical health, sports provide opportunities for social interaction. By playing sports in Turkey, you can make new friends and adopt a healthy lifestyle.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-27T14:03:44Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:52:17Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sports-facilities-and-fitness-membership-fees-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"People working out in a spacious, modern gym in Turkey.","title":"sports-facilities-and-fitness-membership-fees-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'sports-facilities-and-membership-fees-in-turkey' );
