<p class="wp-block-paragraph">De nombreux événements sociaux et festivals sont organisés en Turquie. Vous pouvez participer à diverses activités telles que des traditions locales, des concerts, des expositions d&#8217;art et des événements sportifs.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-06-24T04:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T15:51:25Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/a-student-guide-to-couchsurfing-and-airbnb-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"Student-friendly short-term accommodation in Turkey with cozy room and city view","title":"a-student-guide-to-couchsurfing-and-airbnb-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'fr' AND "slug" = 'guide-du-couchsurfing-et-dairbnb-pour-les-etudiants-en-turquie' );
